otes/the-events-calendar-6-15-6/\">The Events Calendar 6.15.6</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theeventscalendar.com\">The Events Calendar</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Emily Negroni\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4748:\"\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-9d6595d7 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:33.3%\">\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-summary\">Summary</h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"release-label has-normal-font-size\">Maintenance Release</p>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:66.66%\">\n<p class=\"release-summary__overview has-medium-font-size\">The latest version of The Events Calendar includes more accessibility improvements and fixes the Elementor Venue widget to show the map show/hide option with proper styling.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>The Events Calendar 6.15.6 is only compatible with Events Pro 7.7.6 and higher.</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>As always, we recommend <a href=\"https://theeventscalendar.com/knowledgebase/k/creating-and-using-a-wordpress-staging-site/\">testing updates</a> on a staging site first, but it should all be smooth sailing.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-css-opacity\"/>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-9d6595d7 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:33.33%\">\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-fixed\"><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/16.0.1/72x72/2705.png\" alt=\"✅\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /> Fixed</h4>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:66.66%\">\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">Bugs that were squashed in this release:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Elementor Venue widget now shows the map show or hide option with proper styling options.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Enhanced iCal feed timezone definitions include extended DST transition data for better calendar compatibility.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>The onboarding wizard now displays a loading spinner properly while waiting for Event Tickets installation.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Prevents ICS download from redirecting when the List view is disabled.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Adds aria-label for the more events link in month view.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Adjusts aria-label for month view day link to use formatting from TEC settings.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Conditionally removes the template option if Elementor Pro is active to avoid conflicts.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-css-opacity\"/>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-9d6595d7 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:33.33%\">\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-tweaks\"><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/16.0.1/72x72/2699.png\" alt=\"⚙\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /> Tweaks</h4>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:66.66%\">\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">Tweaks in this release:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Adds filters: `tec_events_views_v2_should_redirect`, `tec_events_ical_timezone_extend_years` </li>\n\n\n\n<li>Changes views: `v2/month/calendar-body/day/cell-title`, `v2/month/calendar-body/day/cell`, `v2/month/calendar-body/day/more-events`, `v2/month/mobile-events/mobile-day`, `v2/month/mobile-events/mobile-day/more-events` </li>\n\n\n\n<li>Hide the Event Tickets upsell on the currency page when Event Tickets is enabled.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Introduces subtabs for the Integration settings for better organization.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Updates the Community Addon upsell link to go to the proper page.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-css-opacity\"/>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-9d6595d7 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:33.3%\">\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-translations\"><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/16.0.1/72x72/1f5e3.png\" alt=\"🗣\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /> Translations</h4>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:66.66%\">\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">Updated language files and strings:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>4 new strings added</li>\n\n\n\n<li>75 updated</li>\n\n\n\n<li>0 fuzzied</li>\n\n\n\n<li>0 obsoleted</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theeventscalendar.com/release-notes/the-events-calendar-6-15-6/\">The Events Calendar 6.15.6</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theeventscalendar.com\">The Events Calendar</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:7;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:63:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:3:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:25