(1871, 342, '_elementor_data', '[{\"id\":\"4ad37706\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"237bd3df\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<h4><b>Dobrodo\\u0161li na Let\'s go travel<\\/b>!<\\/h4><div>\\u00a0<\\/div><p>Tvoja avantura po\\u010dinje ovde. U Let\'s go travel, verujemo da putovanje nije samo o destinacijama, ve\\u0107 o nezaboravnim iskustvima koja ostavljaju dubok trag u tvojim uspomenama.<\\/p><h5><b>Za\\u0161to Let\'s go travel?<\\/b><\\/h5><div><b>\\u00a0<\\/b><\\/div><p>Stru\\u010dnost i Posve\\u0107enost: Na\\u0161a turisti\\u010dka agencija je sastavljena od stru\\u010dnjaka sa bogatim iskustvom u industriji putovanja. Posve\\u0107eni smo tome da ti pru\\u017eimo najbolje mogu\\u0107e iskustvo.\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 <span style=\\\"color: var(--tmp-body-font-color); font-family: var(--tmp-primary-font-family); font-size: var(--tmp-primary-font-size); font-weight: var(--tmp-primary-font-weight); letter-spacing: var(--tmp-primary-font-spacing); text-align: var(--text-align); text-transform: var(--tmp-primary-font-transform);\\\">Raznolike Destinacije: Bilo da sanja\\u0161 o belim pe\\u0161\\u010danim pla\\u017eama, avanturama u planinama, fascinantnim gradskim pejza\\u017eima ili kulturolo\\u0161kim iskustvima, Let\'s go travel ima paletu destinacija koje \\u0107e zadovoljiti svaki tvoj ukus.\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 <\\/span><span style=\\\"text-align: var(--text-align); color: var(--tmp-body-font-color); font-family: var(--tmp-primary-font-family); font-size: var(--tmp-primary-font-size); font-weight: var(--tmp-primary-font-weight); letter-spacing: var(--tmp-primary-font-spacing); text-transform: var(--tmp-primary-font-transform);\\\">Prilago\\u0111ene Ture: Shvatamo da su svi putnici jedinstveni. Zato prilago\\u0111avamo na\\u0161e ture i pakete putovanja prema tvojim preferencama i interesovanjima.<\\/span><\\/p><p>Bezbednost na Prvom Mestu: Tvoja bezbednost je na\\u0161 prioritet. Svi na\\u0161i partneri i aktivnosti pa\\u017eljivo su odabrani kako bi se osiguralo da tvoje putovanje bude sigurno i bezbri\\u017eno iskustvo.<\\/p><h5><b>Kako po\\u010deti?<\\/b><\\/h5><p>Istra\\u017ei Destinacije: Pregledaj na\\u0161u ponudu destinacija i prona\\u0111i mesto koje odgovara tvojim \\u017eeljama i interesovanjima.\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 <span style=\\\"text-align: var(--text-align); color: var(--tmp-body-font-color); font-family: var(--tmp-primary-font-family); font-size: var(--tmp-primary-font-size); font-weight: var(--tmp-primary-font-weight); letter-spacing: var(--tmp-primary-font-spacing); text-transform: var(--tmp-primary-font-transform);\\\">Kontaktiraj Nas: Na\\u0161 tim stru\\u010dnjaka za putovanja je ovde da odgovori na sva tvoja pitanja, pru\\u017ei savete i pomogne ti da planira\\u0161 savr\\u0161eno putovanje.\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 <\\/span><span style=\\\"text-align: var(--text-align); color: var(--tmp-body-font-color); font-family: var(--tmp-primary-font-family); font-size: var(--tmp-primary-font-size); font-weight: var(--tmp-primary-font-weight); letter-spacing: var(--tmp-primary-font-spacing); text-transform: var(--tmp-primary-font-transform);\\\">Rezervi\\u0161i Sada: Jednostavno rezervi\\u0161i svoje putovanje online i pripremi se za nezaboravnu avanturu.<\\/span><\\/p><p><b>Dobrodo\\u0161ao\\/la u svet Let\'s go travel, gde tvoje putovanje postaje stvarnost.\\u00a0<\\/b><\\/p><p><b>Spreman\\/na si da krene\\u0161 na put? Let\'s go!<\\/b><\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"032c6e8\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":{\"flex_direction\":\"row\",\"flex_wrap\":\"wrap\",\"flex_gap\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":0,\"column\":\"0\",\"row\":\"0\"}},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"8deee8f\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":{\"flex_direction\":\"column\",\"content_width\":\"full\",\"width\":{\"unit\":\"%\",\"size\":\"33.3333\"}},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"f1685b3\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8081\\/domaci3\\/wordpress-6.4.2\\/wordpress\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/12\\/milanooo.jpg\",\"id\":89,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":true},{\"id\":\"165bc53\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":{\"flex_direction\":\"column\",\"content_width\":\"full\",\"width\":{\"unit\":\"%\",\"size\":\"33.3333\"}},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"ea9baa4\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8081\\/domaci3\\/wordpress-6.4.2\\/wordpress\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/12\\/ven.jpg\",\"id\":80,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":true},{\"id\":\"4a5f4fa\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":{\"flex_direction\":\"column\",\"content_width\":\"full\",\"width\":{\"unit\":\"%\",\"size\":\"33.3333\"}},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"3741c71\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8081\\/domaci3\\/wordpress-6.4.2\\/wordpress\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/12\\/koloseum.jpg\",\"id\":43,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":true},{\"id\":\"7b86464\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":{\"flex_direction\":\"column\",\"content_width\":\"full\",\"width\":{\"unit\":\"%\",\"size\":\"33.3333\"}},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"ad7e93c\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8081\\/domaci3\\/wordpress-6.4.2\\/wordpress\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/12\\/prag.jpg\",\"id\":86,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":true},{\"id\":\"b279930\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":{\"flex_direction\":\"column\",\"content_width\":\"full\",\"width\":{\"unit\":\"%\",\"size\":\"33.3333\"}},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"085c588\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8081\\/domaci3\\/wordpress-6.4.2\\/wordpress\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/12\\/berlin.jpg\",\"id\":187,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"},\"image_size\":\"1536x1536\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":true},{\"id\":\"3e2845e\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":{\"flex_direction\":\"column\",\"content_width\":\"full\",\"width\":{\"unit\":\"%\",\"size\":\"33.3333\"}},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"5e34c29\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8081\\/domaci3\\/wordpress-6.4.2\\/wordpress\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/12\\/pariz.jpg\",\"id\":36,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":true}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"8beee3b\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":{\"flex_direction\":\"column\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"f56baf2\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":\"O nama\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"137b548\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"a75f022\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<div>Turisti\\u010dka agencija Kosmopolit osnovana je 2011. godine. Mlada po sta\\u017eu, zrela po iskustvu tima koji je \\u010dini, posta\\u0107e i osta\\u0107e va\\u0161a agencija. Profesionalna, iskusna, precizna i fleksibilna, diskretna i ozbiljna\\u2026 Onakva kakvu zaslu\\u017eujete. Sa \\u017eeljom da unese i dio svoje kreativnosti u pru\\u017eanju turisti\\u010dkih usluga na ovom tr\\u017ei\\u0161tu, kao i da ponudu obogati nekim novim sadr\\u017eajima nastala je turisti\\u010dka agencija Kosmopolit\\u00a0.<\\/div><p>Visokoobu\\u010deni kadrovi, tehni\\u010dka opremljenost, i pa\\u017eljiv izbor partnera kako u zemlji tako i u inostranstvu, u\\u010dini\\u0107e da va\\u0161e putovanje bude ba\\u0161 onakvo kakvim ste ga i zamislili. Kvalitet servisa bi\\u0107e nam imperativ, a zadovoljstvo klijenata na\\u0161om uslugom zvijezda vodilja u poslovanju.<\\/p><p>U narednom periodu i nakon nebrojeno mnogo uspje\\u0161no organizovanih putovanja \\u0161irom svijeta, pozicionirat \\u0107emo se na tr\\u017ei\\u0161tu me\\u0111u vode\\u0107im turisti\\u010dkim agencijama.<\\/p><p>Turisti\\u010dka ponuda agencije Kosmopolit \\u00a0svrstava se u najraznovrsniju i najpovoljniju. Organizujemo turisti\\u010dke obilaske najve\\u0107ih svjetskih metropola kao \\u0161to su: Istanbul, Prag, Rim, Venecija, Milano, Pariz, Barcelona, Madrid, Be\\u010d, Budimpe\\u0161ta, Minhen, Amsterdam, Lisabon, Moskva, Dubai\\u2026 Kod nas mo\\u017eete na\\u0107i i aran\\u017emane za ljetnu i zimsku sezonu, daleke destinacije, krstarenja, izlete, grupne i individualne programe, avio karte, hotelski smje\\u0161taj, rent a car. Tako\\u0111er, organizujemo studentske i \\u0161kolske ekskurzije, kao i team building putovanja.<\\/p><p>Kori\\u0161tenjem nekoliko globalnih ON-LINE rezervacionih sistema omogu\\u0107i\\u0107emo vam izbor izme\\u0111u gotovo svih registrovanih avio-prijevoznika, sletit \\u0107ete gdje god ima komercionalnih aerodroma, bira\\u0107ete izme\\u0111u 50.000 hotela \\u0161irom planete kao i skoro 30.000 lokacija RAC poslovnica, vi\\u0161e Cruise kompanija\\u2026 Ili mo\\u017eda \\u017eelite avion samo za vas (Air jet), limuzinu sa voza\\u010dem (limousine service), VIP apartmane?<\\/p><p>Rukovodimo se poslovicom da VRIJEDITE ONOLIKO KOLIKO STE DRUGIMA POTREBNI. U\\u010dinite da vrijedimo, zadovoljsto bi\\u0107e i va\\u0161e.<\\/p><p>Napravite dobar izbor, budite na\\u0161 klijent, a mi \\u0107emo u\\u010diniti sve da ukazano povjerenje opravdamo. O\\u010dekujemo va\\u0161e dobronamjerne prijedloge i sugestije, kako bi bili bolji i pribli\\u017eili se onome \\u0161to se zove vrh.<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"3d3442e\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":{\"flex_direction\":\"column\",\"boxed_width\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":1162,\"sizes\":[]},\"min_height\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":511,\"sizes\":[]}},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"89d28fd\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"smartsliderid\":\"4\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"smartslider\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"464e4b6\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":{\"flex_direction\":\"column\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"f3f09e1\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"setti